{"tid":320533,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 詠 琪 帶 囡 囡 見 舊 同 學","createTime":"2017-07-13T14:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T19:21:44.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af60aecec7a96c52fc194e48745e2227e0e6ed35","tid":320533,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:52:45.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）的「好時辰」世界巡迴演唱會，早前就去到美國進行連續兩站演出，順道帶同老公Sergio和囡囡Sofia同行，GiGi表示：「今次除咗係演唱會，更加似舉行同學會，因為很多已經移民嘅舊同學都嚟睇演唱會，我當然要帶Sofia見吓一班auntie。」<br />\n<br />\n同時今次美國之旅另一重點，是Sergio的媽媽和妹妹都有現身，令GiGi十分緊張：「佢哋係第一次睇我演唱會，我準備好一段西班牙文嚟感謝佢哋遠道而來。」另外，她中學的音樂老師亦是座上客：「佢雖然已經70歲，都揸一個鐘頭車嚟睇我演唱會，真係非常感動。」<br />\n<br />\n演出後GiGi就全家人留在當地遊覽，她說：「Sofia今年將會開始返學，以後想一家人去旅行唔係咁容易，趁今次機會就玩吓。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170713/large/13ec4p11a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170713%2Flarge%2F13ec4p11a.jpg&h=ad8e2789&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7935912f232fb955f8c92dd825ed56a6522f5c3","tid":320533,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"身打扮好好勝<br />\n我係西班牙鬥牛實衝住佢撞"},{"pid":"488987a87cfbddc978228e6a54e87519035bf452","tid":320533,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"篇文比樓主del左啲重點？"},{"pid":"50e6f337cb82d0eb55b3b55cb41ca62f4d6a998c","tid":320533,"uid":60028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T20:03:58.000Z","msg":"佢個女平時係咪稱呼佢呀爸做&quot;西班牙老豆&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357f28c206d41e1032c49e40c5d316906e402def","tid":320533,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T20:04:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">s</span></span>"},{"pid":"2349b8d1120cc2cbdcf84623fb3136f7d915bdbf","tid":320533,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score